metadata.name: The Ostal Project x MemoryCollector - Too Many Humans
metadata.description:
Too Many Humans is the new collaboration between The Ostal Project & MemoryCollector. Limited to 10 copies, this piece showcases 30 seconds audio preview. Buyers will unlock HQ 320 kbps MP3 version. Buyers will also receive a link for downloading HD animated MP4 artwork.
The purchase of this NFT goes to support the artists & DAOrecords. Copyright and ownership of the audio is retained by the creators and offers the NFT holder a license for non-commercial, personal use only. Thank you for your support!
